## Limitations

This report is based on available data and articles up to October 2023. The housing market is subject to rapid changes due to economic shifts, policy changes, and unforeseen events such as pandemics. Therefore, the findings may not fully capture the most current trends or future developments in the housing market. Additionally, regional variations in housing markets mean that some findings may not be universally applicable.